    <title>A sharp bound for the Real Waring rank of monomials</title>
    <summary>  In this paper we consider the real Waring rank of monomials. We give a sharp
upper bound for it by establishing a way in which one can take a structured
apolar set for any given monomial. This bound recovers all known cases for the
real rank of monomials as well. Some examples and computations are also
presented in the end of the paper.
</summary>
